================================================================================
                           PROJECT DESCRIPTION
================================================================================

HaleHound-CYD is a multi-protocol offensive security toolkit built for the
ESP32-2432S028 "Cheap Yellow Display" (CYD) platform. It ports the full
ESP32-DIV HaleHound v2.5.0 firmware to the CYD's 2.8" touchscreen form
factor, adding external CC1101 SubGHz, NRF24L01+PA+LNA 2.4GHz, and GPS
radios via the CYD's breakout pins.

HALEHOUND-CYD FEATURES:

  WiFi Attacks:
    - Packet Monitor with real-time frame statistics
    - Beacon Spammer with custom/random SSID flooding
    - WiFi Deauther with network scan and tap-to-attack
    - Probe Sniffer with Evil Twin auto-spawn chain
    - WiFi Scanner with tap-to-Deauth/Clone handoff
    - GARMR Captive Portal (Evil Twin credential harvest)
    - Station Scanner with client enumeration

  Bluetooth Attacks:
    - BLE Jammer (advertisement channel flooding)
    - BLE Spoofer (device identity cloning)
    - BLE Beacon (custom advertisement broadcast)
    - BLE Sniffer (passive traffic analysis)
    - BLE Scanner (device discovery)

  2.4GHz NRF24 Attacks:
    - Channel Scanner
    - Spectrum Analyzer with visual RF display
    - WLAN Jammer (broadband 2.4GHz disruption)
    - Proto Kill (multi-protocol attack suite)

  SubGHz CC1101 Attacks:
    - Signal Replay Attack (record and replay)
    - Brute Force (automated code generation)
    - SubGHz Jammer (wideband disruption)
    - Spectrum Analyzer
    - Saved Profile management

  SIGINT Operations:
    - EAPOL/PMKID Capture (WPA handshake harvesting)
    - Karma Attack (auto-respond probe requests)
    - Wardriving (GPS-tagged AP scanning)
    - Saved Captures browser

  Tools:
    - UART Serial Monitor (hardware hacking terminal)
    - OTA Firmware Update from SD card
    - Touch Calibration utility
    - GPS satellite view with live NMEA data

  Hardware Support:
    - ESP32-2432S028 CYD 2.8" (primary, fully tested)
    - ESP32-3248S035 CYD 3.5" (pin defines ready, untested)
    - Full touchscreen navigation
    - CC1101 SubGHz radio (external)
    - NRF24L01+PA+LNA 2.4GHz radio (external)
    - GT-U7 / NEO-6M GPS module (external)
    - MicroSD card (built-in slot)
    - All radios at maximum TX power


